FBIS3-33882 "drnes021_r_94005" FBIS-NES-94-021 Document Type:Daily Report 1 Feb 1994 India Spokesman Denies Shooting Report BK3101150994 Delhi All India Radio Network in English 1430 GMT 31 Jan 94 BK3101150994 Delhi All India Radio Network Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] An official spokesman today strongly refuted press reports that the union home minister's helicopter was fired at during his visit to Doda yesterday. The spokesman said that no such incident concerning the home minister's helicopter took place during his visit to Doda and Kishtwar yesterday. However, militants fired a few rounds from a very distant place from Doda town, which were not aimed at the helicopter or any particular object. Moreover, the home minister's helicopter landed much later than this random firing.
